'''利卡西'''（舊名：雅多維爾/Jadotville）是[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]東南部的城市，位於[[上加丹加省|上加丹加省]]，2005年人口367,000<ref>[http://www.reliefweb.int/rw/RWB.NSF/db900SID/LSGZ-6GPF2E "DWW bought a building for RADEM maternity in Congo"] Doctors Worldwide, 28 September 2005, from ''ReliefWeb'', accessed 28 March 2009</ref>。

利卡西是工業中心，以開採[[銅|銅]]礦和[[鈷|鈷]]礦的採礦業為主<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/7965221.stm Harding, Andrew (27 March 2009)"Slowdown blights DR Congo economy"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/7965221.stm |date=20090330020521 }} ''BBC News'', accessed 27 March 2009</ref><ref>Rorison, Sean (2008) "Likasi" ''Congo: Democratic Republic and Republic'' Bradt Travel Guides, Chalfont St. Peter, England, [http://books.google.com/books?id=cXJyOKBqJZwC&pg=RA1-PA143 pp. 143-145] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=cXJyOKBqJZwC&pg=RA1-PA143 |date=20140107174605 }} ISBN 1-84162-233-8</ref>，國家鐵路系統在利卡西設站，使其成為鄰近地區的交通樞紐。

